DEPRECATED
==========
This directory's role prompts have been REBUILT as v3 charters under
`shared/charters/` per design decision #7 (industry-anchored charters).
See `lib/role-prompts/README.md` for the per-file migration map.

The legacy files remain readable until Wave 6 runs `git rm -rf lib/`.
New code MUST import from `shared/charters/`, not here.
